42:45.040 --> 42:47.869
♪ Sometime when it's late
and I'm a little hungry ♪

42:47.913 --> 42:50.306
♪ I heat up
some old stale beans ♪

42:50.350 --> 42:52.352
♪ Open up a can of sardines

42:52.395 --> 42:53.919
♪ Eat crackers and dream

42:53.962 --> 42:57.705
♪ About somebody
to cook for me ♪

42:57.749 --> 43:00.665
♪ Too much time,
too much time ♪

